    "ts": "2026-03-20T20:59:05+00:00",
    "headline": "Trump Suit Against Capital One Dismissed But Can Be Refiled",
    "summary": "During a hearing Friday, US District Judge Roy Altman in Miami granted Capital One’s request to dismiss the suit filed by President Donald Trump’s sprawling real estate company, which had accused the bank of closing hundreds of its business accounts out of animus toward conservatives in a process known as de-banking.  Altman, a Trump appointee, said the complaint was “deficient” for numerous reasons but he nevertheless gave the Trump Organization a chance to file a new one.",
    "url": "https://finance.yahoo.com/news/trump-suit-against-capital-one-200454780.html",
